<name>DIFFERENTIAL CASE</name>
<para id="RM00000282A000X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="AX13J-01" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM00000282A000X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM00000282A000X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___0000BNX00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT DIFFERENTIAL SIDE GEAR BACKLASH</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Hold the differential case in a vise between aluminum plates.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C083562" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Do not overtighten the vise.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Place a dial indicator on the tip of the side gear tooth at a right angle.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Hold the pinion gear in the differential case and measure the backlash of the side gear.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard backlash</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>0 to 0.15 mm (0 to 0.0059 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<table>
<title>Thrust washer thickness</title>
